ation the helix platform offers a revolutionary laser scanning sensor that allows faster and more precise measurement of complex geometries the unique patented helix technology scans parts with stationary sensors by utilizing its internal mems technology this provides fully programmable line length density and sweepscan field of measurement more details → gdt – validate to design intent perceptron leverages d design data to provide realtime geometric dimensioning  tolerancing gdt information that can be applied to any production part or assembly all measurement calculations are integral repeatable and traceable to ansi  iso standards configure to cad – measure sooner fully utilizing cad data perceptron can deliver engineered measurement solutions faster and more efficiently d data from your plant and product design can be utilized for robot reach studies and robot path programming before your first assembly is built global solutions local support our customers are global and demand missioncritical production metrology solutions with local support uniquely perceptron owns support locations in  countries more details → next prev  automated enterprise metrology solutions perceptron offers an extensive portfolio of dimensional gauging and inspection products along with robotic guidance gap  flush measurement and d laser scanning solutions with over  years of experience perceptron can be your enterprise metrology partner   dimensional gauging precision noncontact automated dimensional measurement and gauging solutions provide realtime part assembly and process information for inline or nearline quality control applications robot guidance robot guidance solutions provide realtime adaptive feedback ensuring missioncritical manufacturing operations are automatically corrected for process and product variations gap  flush measurement automated noncontact inspection solutions measure gap and flush features for quality validation or process optimization systems can be installe