chenglish uk medical metrology solutions perceptron inc home investors careers register for news medical metrology solutions home → industries → medical metrology solutions medical technology continues to advance with associated equipment becoming ever more sophisticated with life expectancy continuing to increase and our individual demands growing whether it be the equipment used in surgery or prosthetic implants industrial metrology is critical to equipment reliability and performance during its manufacture perceptron is a leader supplier of industrial metrology solutions to the medical equipment sector   world headquarters perceptron incplymouth mi  phone  email infoperceptroncom stay connected rss facebook email youtube linkedin helix hdr sensor perceptrons latest helix hdr high dynamic range sensor produces a thinner laser line and offers higher measurement resolution ideally suited for the inspection of complex machined parts the higher laser power also allows more complex measuring applications including inspection of highly reflective metallic surfaces such as machined aluminum castings found in the aerospace and automotive sectors more information deutschenglish uk helix d scanning sensors  perceptron inc perceptron inc home investors careers register for news helix d scanning sensors home → helix d scanning sensors helix™ is perceptron’s family of next generation d scanning sensors incorporating mems technology offering the world’s first fully programmable laser scanner the laser line quantity density length and orientation characteristics are all user configurable and eliminate the necessity to physically move the scanner over the part during scanning all scanning motion is contained within the patented helix smart sensor dramatically improving quality and accuracy of scanned data it also allows you to capture multiple part features in one sensor position ensuring both accurate and repeatable measurement results helix contains an imbedded accelerometer to determine realtime sensor orientation it was developed specially for advanced robotic inspection applications where the robot moves the sensor to discrete measuring positions and collects all required measurement data helixhdr high dynamic range the advanced performance helixhdr smart sensor offers high power and extended dynamic range providing adjustable power up to the maximum permitted for a class r laser helixhdr produces a thinner laser line and offers higher measurement resolution ideally suited for the inspection of complex machined parts and also exports enhanced d point clouds the higher power also allows more complex measuring applications including inspection of highly reflective metallic surfaces such as machined aluminum castings found in the automotive and aerospace sectors for more information about perceptron’s helix d laser scanning sensor family download our brochure below your name required company required your email required your phone number               world headquarters perceptron incplymouth mi  phone  email infoperceptroncom stay connected rss facebook email youtube linkedin helix hdr sensor perceptrons latest helix hdr high dynamic range sensor produces a thinner laser line and offers higher measurement resolution ideally suited for the inspection of complex machined parts the higher laser power also allows more complex measuring applications including inspection of highly reflective metallic surfaces such as machined aluminum castings found in the aerospace and automotive sectors more information deutschenglish uk perceptron  automated enterprise metrology solutions perceptron inc home investors careers register for news about us home → about us automated enterprise metrology solutions perceptron offers an extensive portfolio of dimensional gauging and inspection products along with robotic guidance gap  flush measurement and d laser scanning solutions with over  years of experience perceptron can be your enterprise metrology partner globally companies rely on perceptron’s metrology solutions to assist in managing their complex manufacturing processes to improve quality shorten product launch times and reduce costs more than  systems  perceptron measuring sensors and over  coord coordinate measuring machines are in active daily use worldwide headquartered in plymouth michigan usa with subsidiary operations in brazil china the czech republic france germany india italy spain japan singapore slovakia spain and the uk our mission to be the global leader in supplying advanced metrology technology by helping our customers to identify and solve their measurement and quality problems our story perceptron nasdaqprcp was founded in  by graduates of the general motors institute formerly gmi and now kettering university working closely with the automotive industry they analyzed and comprehended the damaging effects of process variation on complex product assembly operations and concluded “a process which cannot be measured can never be effectively controlled or optimized” through revolutionary machine vision and pioneering engineering efforts they created a unique and innovative measurement solution that not only allowed fast and efficient containment of quality problems as they occurred but also provided the ability to proactively seekout and reduce process variation the final result was groundbreaking – the first viable inprocess  dimensional measurement solution capable of being deployed in the harshest of manufacturing environments world headquarters perceptron incplymouth mi  phone  email infoperceptroncom stay connected rss facebook email youtube linkedin helix hdr sensor perceptrons latest helix hdr high dynamic range sensor produces a thinner laser line and offers higher measurement resolution ideally suited for the inspection of complex machined parts the higher laser power also allows more complex measuring applications including inspection of highly reflective metallic surfaces such as machined a